rows.label: qst100202_msg0001
rows.name:
W-w-wait... Please calm down, mo...
Just wait a little longer, mo...

rows.label: qst100202_msg0003
rows.name:
If you won't back down, then
I'll just have to show you
the power of Superbia!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0004
rows.name:
The power of Superbia? What power
does a sinking Divine Beast have?

rows.label: qst100202_msg0005
rows.name:
Hah! You country bumpkin with
your prehistoric technology...

rows.label: qst100202_msg0006
rows.name:
Hyaaa... They won't stop, mo...
Driver-san, please do something, mo!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0101
rows.name:
What man would back down
after having his homeland
insulted like that?!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0102
rows.name:
It seems I'll have to beat
the difference in our power
into your body...

rows.label: qst100202_msg0104
rows.name:
In that case, both sides are at fault,
mo! Driver-san! Go get 'em, mo!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0201
rows.name:
Huh? What're you doing? Are you
trying to steal the Delta Box
that I won in the auction?

rows.label: qst100202_msg0202
rows.name:
What did you say?! I
will not allow that...

rows.label: qst100202_msg0203
rows.name:
Enough of this nonsense!
I'll take you on along with
that Superbian thief!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0204
rows.name:
This is getting complicated, mo...
Driver-san! Don't lose, mo!
